patthana16.64:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ saññojanaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho nosaññojano dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.64:2.1_0: Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.64:3.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ganthaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho nogantho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe….
patthana16.64:4.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ oghaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho noogho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe….
patthana16.64:5.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ yogaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho noyogo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.64:6.1_0: Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.64:7.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ nīvaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho nonīvaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.64:8.1_0: Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.64:9.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ parāmāsaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho noparāmāso dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.64:10.1_0: Hetuyā cha, ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
